{"type": "article", "id": 16474, "title": "月亮茶杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-23T06:40:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 113, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135544ajks3MWhU5qTvHpK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t产品设计里常常使用月亮元素，这套陶杯则借用了月亮的盈缺。随着水的注入，黑色的陶杯呈现由缺到盈的过程，反之，当一点一点喝掉杯子里的水时，则也是由盈到缺的过程。韩国设计工作室 Tale 设计了这个杯子，将杯子的底部做了一定弧度的填充，配合传统的白色米酒会非常有意境。有大小两种型号，分别售价 30 美元、 24 美元，<a href=\"http://www.tale-design.com/?page_id=1978\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143725mRCbtZoeyDs8wj3J.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261437251J24yYbDHkuRES7M.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"368\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51040222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143725G6WDJsh7eOgUd51l.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"337\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.46740638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143726rMz2tu8HcimGaSbR.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"328\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45492372\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}